.TH "pmcraid_alloc_sglist" 9 "pmcraid_alloc_sglist" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pmcraid_alloc_sglist \- Allocates memory for a SG list
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct pmcraid_sglist *" pmcraid_alloc_sglist
.BI "(int buflen "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "buflen" 12
buffer length
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Allocates a DMA'able buffer in chunks and assembles a scatter/gather
list.

Return value
pointer to sglist / NULL on failure
